{
  "name": "RPlog_Dareus_Meets_A_Doppelganger",
  "title": "Dareus Meets a Doppelganger",
  "summary": "Aboard his Sith flagship Predator, the apprentice Captain Antoine Dareus is confronted by a Force-projected doppelganger of Luke Skywalker, conjured from light-years away aboard the Refrain of Anshalar. Skywalker admits he has come on reconnaissance, and the two trade barbed philosophical clashes over the dark side, the Republic, and Dareus's master Malign as the Jedi probes the ship's history, uncovering the torture of Dareus's wife Serenella and hints about the dead world of Cochran. Dareus orders a ship-wide lockdown and unleashes Malign's hidden combat droids, and the doppelganger duels them through corridor after corridor, deliberately wrecking the ship and absorbing every detail of the droids' design and numbers. Believing he has captured and felled the great Skywalker, Dareus kneels to claim the lightsaber, only for the doppelganger and its weapon to dissolve into nothing, the whole intrusion having been an elaborate intelligence-gathering ruse. Humiliated and enraged, Dareus orders an evacuation of the Cochran facility, while the real Skywalker, his mission accomplished, jumps the Refrain to hyperspace with Seth Senesca at the helm.",
